name: Tank Go Boom
description:
The M1 Abrams SEPv3 is the main battle tank in the United States Army. Its armor is near impenetrable, it weapons systems unmatched in lethality. Capable of laying direct fire on a target 5,000 meters away, this weapons platform is the pinnacle of American military lethality and is perfect to be the first subject minted by AllPowerNFT. This particular piece was photographed in action at Fort Hood, Texas, during a TABLE 6 Live Fire Gunnery.

Purchasing this piece not only shows support for your men and women in uniform, but also be ensured that all proceeds will go to a military service member. That is our promise at AllPowerNFT.
